name: vscode-textobjects
description: inspired by tree sitter. this is the vscode implementation of object selection

vscode-textobjects.vimEnabled.description: Activates keyboard motions to select, delete, go to, yank and delete selections

vscode-textobjects.copyOnDelete.description: Activates keyboard motions to select, delete, go to, yank and delete selections

scripts.compile: npm run check-types && npm run lint && node esbuild.js
scripts.package: npm run check-types && npm run lint && node esbuild.js --production
scripts.pretest: npm run compile-tests && npm run compile && npm run lint
